            "jpText": "ファンたちの声援を背に受けながら\r\n『宝塚記念』を走り切った。\n惜しくも負けてしまったが――",
            "enText": "She finished the Takarazuka Kinen with \nthe cheers of her fans behind her. \nAlthough she lost the race…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 142,
                    "pathId": 9111806166385115399
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 153,
                    "pathId": -4814940898249029360
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2203307760662923000,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "たくさんの観客たちを笑顔にした\r\n彼女は、ようやく求め続けた\n“青いバラ”になることができたのだった。",
            "enText": "She made many spectators smile, and was \nfinally able to become the \"blue rose\" she \nhad always wanted.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 142,
                    "pathId": 7798256308471633127
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 153,
                    "pathId": -19533706218980663
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7157747653699681993,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "レースを終えたライスシャワーは、\r\nミホノブルボンやメジロマックイーンが\n出走する『有馬記念』に出たいと希望する。",
            "enText": "After the race, Rice Shower hopes to run in \nthe Arima Kinen, where Mihono Bourbon and \nMejiro McQueen will be running.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "coloredText": [
                {
                    "jpText": "有馬記念",
                    "enText": "Arima Kinen"
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 142,
                    "pathId": 7631512882350675838
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 153,
                    "pathId": -6386807214933906729
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 238,
