            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『宝塚記念』と同じように、\r\nファン投票で人気を集めたウマ娘しか\n出走できない『有馬記念』。",
            "enText": "Just like the Takarazuka Kinen, only the most \npopular horse girl in the fan vote can run in \nthe Arima Kinen.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 238,
                    "pathId": -734932140660803121
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 252,
